    • Field Detail

      • ID_2_CLASS_MAP

        protected static com.jiowa.template.bean.ID2ClassMap ID_2_CLASS_MAP
        This map delivers the corresponding template bean class for a given (sub)template identifier. This ensures that (sub)template filtering works even in those cases where the user might choose to obfuscate his template beans (for whatever reason).

      • parent

        protected CaseComponent_jCOLIBRI_jgt parent
        Parent template bean (also used for value propagation). If values or subtemplates are not set in this template, the initializations are propagated from the parent bean.

    • Constructor Detail

      • foreachAttributeList

        protected foreachAttributeList(CaseComponent_jCOLIBRI_jgt parent)
        Constructor for foreachAttributeList with a reference to parent bean. The parent bean is used for automatic value propagation which works for variable values as well as for subtemplates.
        Parameters:
        parent - parent bean for value propagation
